00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:20,050
They are going that way. Hurry up.

306
00:26:20,050 --> 00:26:21,910
We can't lose them.

307
00:26:21,910 --> 00:26:23,570
Okay, yes. All right.

308
00:26:23,570 --> 00:26:25,080
