00:42:25,190 --> 00:42:29,170
You really don't know what can happen in life.

448
00:42:29,170 --> 00:42:31,710
Grandma Cheon Duk you're a senior...

449
00:42:31,710 --> 00:42:34,080
in... influant—

450
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:35,920
- Inflation. 
 - Yes!

451
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,340
Who would have known...

452
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:39,800
that you would get so popular through that.

